  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Brand Promotions Rep",
  "description": "<h2><strong>Brand Promotions Representative</strong></h2><p>At <strong>Vision Organisation</strong>, we work with established brands to deliver effective on-ground promotions through events, roadshows, and customer engagement campaigns.<br />This role offers hands-on exposure to brand marketing while working closely with a supportive team in a fast-paced, people-focused environment.</p><h3><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Support the execution of live events, roadshows, and promotional campaigns</p></li><li><p>Engage customers through professional, face-to-face interactions</p></li><li><p>Represent client brands accurately and positively in public settings</p></li><li><p>Work collaboratively with team members to ensure smooth campaign delivery</p></li><li><p>Develop practical skills in marketing, sales, and customer engagement through on-the-job learning</p></li></ul><h3><strong>What We Offer</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Full training provided (no prior experience required)</p></li><li><p>Performance-based development with clear growth pathways</p></li><li><p>Exposure to a variety of campaigns and working locations</p></li><li><p>Ongoing coaching, mentorship, and team support</p></li></ul><h3><strong>This Role Is Suitable For Individuals Who</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Are comfortable interacting with people or are keen to develop this skill</p></li><li><p>Are reliable, proactive, and open to learning</p></li><li><p>Enjoy active, on-the-ground work environments</p></li><li><p>Can commit to a full-time role</p></li></ul><h3><strong>How to Apply</strong></h3><p>If you are interested in gaining hands-on experience in brand promotions and live events, we welcome your application.</p><p>📱 <strong>WhatsApp:</strong> 9820 2507<br />💬 <strong>Telegram:</strong> @nitsualim</p>",
